            "set generic changes."
        ],
        "lessonsLearned": [
            "The graph of the quantity “books” is a straight line headed upwards. This type of behavior is called “linear growth.”",
            "The simplest model that exhibits linear growth is exactly like the one you just constructed: An accumulator with a",
            "parameter whose value is repeatedly added to the accumulator’s value."
